{"tid":1542810,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳智庫：近千個被封Twitter五毛賬戶 為打資訊戰散佈假新聞至少2年","createTime":"2019-09-05T03:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T03:48:45.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"732c8149b034619c489cec7ed7fa390a88965ba3","tid":1542810,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"社交網站Twitter早前封鎖大批發佈假新聞抹黑本港反送中運動的賬戶，澳洲智庫研究發現，有940個被封的中國賬戶，是多年來針對中共批評者並散佈假新聞行動的一環。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲戰略政策研究所（ASPI）表示，徹查過被封鎖的Twitter賬戶所發出的360萬條推文，認為這些賬戶散佈假新聞的行動已持續至少2年，主要是針對著名的反共評論員或劍指中共的批評。<br />\n<br />\n最激烈的資訊戰是針對中國億萬富翁郭文貴，他被指控貪污後流亡海外，國際刑警2017年按北京要求對他發出紅色通緝令後數天，針對他的Twitter資訊「洗板」就開始。智庫發現618個賬號中，有3.87萬條直接針對郭文貴的推文，並注意到圍繞「郭文貴與中國政府鬧翻」的活動突然急增。針對郭文貴的推文內容包括攻擊他的人格，或批評他與白宮前首席智囊班農（Steve Bannon）有關係。<br />\n<br />\nASPI報告指：「這是利用濫發訊息的賬戶廣傳資訊，影響一個以影響力招攬生意的網絡。」2017年哈佛大學的研究亦發現，北京每年都有聘人在中國社交網製造多達4.48億條假帖文和評論。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter和Facebook上月關閉逾20萬個假賬戶，指它們在「國家支持」下詆毀支持本港民主運動的人，「蓄意具體地試圖在香港散佈政治紛爭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190905/60008918?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60008918%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6rubPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=cdc23a9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F60008918%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=e088d0d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190905/60008918?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"4730f3cbb1531fd7ef18cde5d50f18fabcfecc9c","tid":1542810,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:36:47.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"959f255e750a69d8b2f3fd80e5b5349960649780","tid":1542810,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}